item.title: Let It Be | Beatles
item.description: All instruments recorded by me (big ups to my mum for the backing vocals though) (: I hope you all like, I put a lot of effort into this, and I know it is far from Beatles quality but I have definitely progressed in terms of my own recording techniques and experimentation.
